;W[rs]LB[pr:1][qr:2][qs:3][sr:4][rs:5]C[Dia.1 Correct

White should cut at 1, but you probably already saw that move.  However, the next move is the most important.  After Black plays the dansu at 2, White needs to play 3 to set up the snapback and put Black in dansu.  Now White can play 5 and Black is dead.
\lang1042\f1\fs18

])
(;CR[qr]AW[oo][ro][so][pp][qp][nq][oq][sq][nr][pr][ns]AB[rp][sp][pq][qq][rq][or][qr][os]
