;B[sr]LB[ps:1][sr:2]CR[qr]C[Dia.2 A mistake

If you just take the stones then you are letting Black get away.  White 1 is a mistake.  Black can now play 2 and make two eyes.\lang1042\f1\fs18

])
(;AW[oo][ro][so][pp][qp][nq][oq][sq][nr][ns]AB[rp][sp][pq][qq][rq][or][os]
