;B[pr]LB[rr:1][qr:2][qs:3][sr:4][rs:5][pr:6]C[Dia.3 Bik

Playing immediately on the inside will only lead to mutual life in the corner.  When White plays 1, Black will block at 2 and then play at 4.  Up to Black 6, we see that it is Bik, meaning Black lives in mutual life.
\lang1042\f1\fs18

